            <section class="content-section" id="problem">
                <h2>User Problem</h2>
                <p>
                    Implementation, marketing, and business teams all needed one place to define data in a Data Catalog. Clean data needed to flow into tracking plans which connect directly into Rudderstack. 
                </p>
                <p>Building tracking plans into Rudderstack allowed our users to use it as a single source of truth that enforced schemas at ingestion, reducing data catalog clutter and upkeep overhead.</p>          
