                    <li>We should rely on our API (not a templated google sheet) and work as closely as possible with ENG to prioritize automation</li>
                    <li>Newer, highly-flexible and interactive UI's like linear and notion were gaining trendiness, and Tracking Plans presented a good case to move in that direction</li>
                </ul>
